cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: panelforge-figures
abstract: >-
  Modality-first, publication-grade figure system for systems biology and
  computational biophysics, with an embedded Claude Code skill for agentic
  bootstrap inside any manuscript repository. Ships 471 statistically
  contract-bound recipes across 20 modalities, an agent-discoverable recipe
  index, provenance + reproducibility tooling, venue/bias/cross-reference
  auditors, and a privacy-by-construction data-class safety layer.
type: software
